@startuml
title Context Diagram - RFID Tracking System (As-Built)

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  BorderColor #2F4858
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #B26A00
}

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #EAF4FF
  BorderColor #2F4858
}

actor "Super Admin\n(`SUPER_ADMIN`)" as SA
actor "Admin\n(`ADMIN`)" as AD
actor "Warehouse Manager\n(`WAREHOUSE_MANAGER`)" as WM
actor "Staff\n(`STAFF`)" as ST
actor "RFID Reader\nST-H103 UHF" as Reader
actor "Customer Location\n(HOTEL / RESORT /\nSPA / CUSTOMER)" as Customer

rectangle "RFID Tracking System" as System {
  rectangle "Web Dashboard" as Web
  rectangle "Mobile App" as Mobile
  rectangle "Backend API\n+ Socket.IO" as API
  database "PostgreSQL" as DB
  rectangle "Redis Cache" as Redis

  Web --> API
  Mobile --> API
  API --> DB
  API --> Redis
}

SA --> Web : user management,\ndashboard summary,\nfull system access
AD --> Web : manage category,\nproduct, tag, location,\ninventory, transfer
AD --> Mobile : live scan,\norders, sessions
WM --> Web : orders, transfers,\ninventory, activity logs
WM --> Mobile : sessions, scans,\nconfirm transfer
ST --> Web : read catalog,\nlogs theo policy
ST --> Mobile : create order,\nsession, scan
Reader --> Mobile : BLE EPC + RSSI
API --> Customer : lưu destination cho\nWAREHOUSE_TO_CUSTOMER

note bottom of System
Current source is tag-centric:
core entities are Tag, Transfer, Order,
Session, Scan, ActivityLog.
end note

note right of Web
Dashboard summary REST endpoint
is guarded by CASL `read Dashboard`
and effectively belongs to SUPER_ADMIN.
Moi websocket client hop le deu join scan:live.
Socket room `admin:dashboard`
is currently keyed by JWT role ADMIN.
end note

note right of Customer
No customer portal in v1.
Customer is represented as
destination location only.
end note

@enduml
